{
  "stem": "16214.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But they would be vehemently against you if you would even suggest something like that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, it's-- they-- they were very [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] uneducated when it really came to their own religion.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you can't help it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You have these sort of prejudices from a childhood, when you raised in this type of atmosphere.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't recall hearing very much about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "However, my father-- my other father, Stanczak-- was-- he belonged to the so-called Armia Krajowa, AK, which is the military unit-- national military unit which was basically fighting the Germans at first, during the war-- later on, fighting the Russians who came to Poland and fighting the Jews.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father was caught, actually, after the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's why my mother had hardly any dealings-- my real mother, when she was looking for me, she had hardly any dealings with my other father because he was always in hiding in post-war Poland, in 1945.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's because he was in that group.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had to hide and they had to support themselves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And basically, they would support themselves by-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you know, by going after banks, because that's where the money is.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was basically caught robbing a bank, and put in-- into jail in early-- in about-- I think in 1947 or so.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Krosniewice?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, in-- in this town where you were with this-- this other family.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in Lodz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was a large city.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Lodz is probably-- at the time, I think the second-largest city in Poland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know exactly what its-- what is the ranking of it at the moment, but it's a large city.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
